data.text: Cohocton is listed in the Cities Category for Steuben County in the state of New York. Cohocton is displayed on the "Wayland" USGS topo map. The latitude and longitude coordinates (GPS waypoint) of Cohocton are 42.5022907 (North), -77.5072102 (West) and the approximate elevation is 1,319 feet (402 meters) above sea level. If you are interested in visiting Cohocton you can print the free topographic map, terrain map, satellite/aerial images, and other maps using the link above. The location, topography, nearby roads and trails, and towns around Cohocton (City) can be seen in the layers of this interactive map. If you have already visited New York's Cohocton in Steuben County, the nearest Cities are listed above for your consideration.
